# LangGraph ETL Pipeline: Visual Overview

This document provides both a high-level conceptual infographic and a technical breakdown of how your data flows through the application.

## 🎨 Conceptual Infographic
![LangGraph ETL Pipeline Infographic](/C:/Users/Nethra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8d40048b-6c27-476f-9213-d7cf354af545/langgraph_etl_infographic_1775626298990.png)

